# Used by tools that respect the `ignore` crate (cargo-machete, ripgrep, fd).
# Vendored third-party code lives here — its dependency hygiene is the
# upstream maintainer's responsibility, not ours, and walking these trees
# from the workspace root drowns the real audit results in noise.
#
# Override locally with `rg --no-ignore`, `fd --no-ignore`, or by passing
# explicit paths to cargo-machete (e.g. `cargo machete vendor/sockudo-ws`).
*
